claims.text:
An apparatus for improving heat dissipation in electronic devices, characterized in that it comprises:
a dynamic learning model (201) that adapts its architecture based on real-time performance feedback;
a hybrid data processing approach (202) combining both structured and unstructured data seamlessly;
an ethical decision-making module (203) to ensure AI decisions adhere to predefined ethical guidelines and norms;
a self-repair mechanism (204) that identifies and corrects errors in its algorithms autonomously;
quantum computing principles (205) to enhance processing speed and efficiency in data handling; and
a cross-platform integration framework (206) that allows the AI to operate across different operating systems and hardware seamlessly.

